{"tid":1519530,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"到底做乜個個話聽日係最後一戰","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T16:09:53.000Z","uid":53842,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7f0415e931b345d5ff30dfbe24e0839c735a4066","tid":1519530,"uid":53842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:04:42.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，一個都未爭取到，最乜撚嘢後一戰？<br />\n我唔理話最後一戰嗰啲係人係鬼，it&rsquo;s just a normal day for us <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每個星期都有夢發架啦，依家你哋講最後一戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後一戰呢個terms，和理巴打就嚇親唔夠膽出嚟，勇武既巴打聽到就好似真係整裝待發準備聽日係最後一場戰爭咁,咁你地即係送勇武巴打去死？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冷靜啲</span></span>，諗一諗，聽日全部人夢照發，但保持冷靜，溫和既同勇武既都要識走位，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">留得青山在真係唔怕會冇柴燒</span></span>，人數嘅嘢，需知道真係小一個就少一個，玩轉數，玩反應，玩返香港人聰明嘅特質，講咁耐，都係做返我哋平時應該要做嘅嘢姐<br />\n<br />\n都係果句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆，不篤灰，一齊守護香港</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f7e9f3e3fcda74a6a7e3915c09b7445e67063e7b","tid":1519530,"uid":53842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:06:16.000Z","msg":"推佢老母484"},{"pid":"9074ba9b236535aaaa5445278e18b881a30656bf","tid":1519530,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:06:36.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a h