43,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:09:47.000Z","msg":"大家唔係約定好 贏嘅時候 要除低口罩煲底相見咩<br />\n仲未到嗰個時候呀 仲未係最後呀<br />\n一齊堅持到贏唯止<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">約定大家 光復到香港嗰一刻 煲底見</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n[小心風向]最後一戰？？？？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1519458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1519458</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"241b5ad8a855a0413bce93ae70bba438e0b43258","tid":1519530,"uid":53842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46b8bd5ecf5d4188014fa256dfab600254df92b6","tid":1519530,"uid":110332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:07:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">10月1號都未到最咩後一戰！對家就真係想係最後一戰，唔洗拖到10月1</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:09:49.000Z","msg":"同意，林鄭真係恨不得一獲打鳩盡所有人，冷靜啲，諗一諗，夢照發但要play smart"},{"pid":"9ae475e4a4981cd851a8aa532dcf10d6b1e8c668","tid":1519530,"uid":212441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:11:04.000Z","msg":"保持冷静"},{"pid":"d121ca604a72125845f1cd7d1ec65e4e9d3a8e86","tid":1519530,"uid":53842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:12:39.000Z","msg":"推佢老母484"},{"pid":"a060cfb9322f4240903b6657c0ee6e951410d946","tid":1519530,"uid":206703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:13:41.000Z","msg":"抗爭活動從來都係長期戰爭 一日未成功一日唔會有最後一戰 有既都係失敗既結局<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人冷靜啲<br />\n唔好俾白色恐怖嚇到<br />\n一怯 對家就贏</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"fa531c2ad6de78b267f305996587cb50293cc4ea","tid":1519530,"uid":134744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:18:06.000Z","msg":"大家真係要冷靜<br />\n唔好比憤怒同仇恨影響判斷<br />\n聽日唔係最後一戰<br />\n抗爭仲有好長嘅路<br />\n只要我哋唔放棄<br />\n總有一日我哋會贏<br />\n無論如何聽日港見"},{"pid":"798d78de8cd1eb7846835784f3db90b82daf6b3b","tid":1519530,"uid":53842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:30:18.000Z","msg":"而家林奠指撚住自己個鼻同你地講聽日掂到我當你地贏，掂唔到當你地輸？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 某程度上來講，五個訴求，我哋一個都冇爭取到，自古以黎，除非你夠雷夠姜夠疊馬可以一晚改朝換代，如果唔係，冇一個抗爭係可以唔需要時間，所以我哋更加要發揮我哋嘅轉數抗爭到底。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「緣督以為經，可以保身，可以全生，可以養親，可以盡年。」</span></span>"},{"pid":"9b82fdbfb83adfc31d8edfeb2b0116997ddcd794","tid":1519530,"uid":53842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:30:35.000Z","msg":"同我推到所有人都見到"},{"pid":"33597b1dbe95dc1168b958aab71db8459b14888e","tid":1519530,"uid":237177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:31:41.000Z","msg":"話831 end game既係咪喬裝"},{"pid":"27fe26d3a60679368fd7608e8c674ebc176c6650","tid":1519530,"uid":117737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"f9f2655c71c53266359b75f962a0d1b28d1007bb","tid":1519530,"uid":53842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33597b1dbe95dc1168b958aab71db8459b14888e","tid":1519530,"uid":237177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:31:41.000Z","msg":"話831 end game既係咪喬裝"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:38:52.000Z","msg":"呢個時候，話知佢係唔係喬裝，我哋要用盡我哋所有辦法去提醒真正嘅巴打絲打"},{"pid":"574cd41e5a75435f43b0ac69e48cab3b28e8e371","tid":1519530,"uid":53842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9f2655c71c53266359b75f962a0d1b28d1007bb","tid":1519530,"uid":53842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33597b1dbe95dc1168b958aab71db8459b14888e","tid":1519530,"uid":237177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:31:41.000Z","msg":"話831 end game既係咪喬裝"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:38:52.